Name: RoboMatch
About the game: The game type three in a row with robots, galaxies and stores. The player armed robots. Rearrange chips that the player shoots at the enemy. After the turn of a player - the progress of the enemy. Many weapons (eight guns, lasers, eight, eight rocket launchers). A large number of additional equipment (generators, shields, armor, coolers, batteries, ...) 6 robots for the player and 5 for the enemy. 83 levels.
